Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:27.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm bringing you a yearly project
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:32.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2022 Prank Ranking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:34.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:35.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's that time of year again
