Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first one was you \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:44.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I did both 2014 and 2015
