Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been allowed to prank anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've done my share of screwing people over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:55.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a time during one prank
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:59.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That I was the one pranking, but also being pranked
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:02.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is also this process
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:06.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The feeling of being flipped when wrestling to make a four-figure leg lock \N -A reversal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:07.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I realized it I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the one who always gets screwed, so why are you screwing someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:11.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
