Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the 2021 King of being pranked
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He has failed to win a 2nd time in a row
