Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:06.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai is 2022's King of Being Pranked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:10.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the result
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:12.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this group of funny people
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with Joy?  \N-It's impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of pranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really awesome to be on the list with these guys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And he's been on the list 5 times so far
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, and at the top of the list
