Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, one day in January
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We reported the results to Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:52.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:58.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For the year 2022, you are the person that has been pranked the most
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:00.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have I been pranked so many times?
