Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's true, now that I think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:13.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I used to read scripts for hours without realizing they were just for a setup
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:20.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai will go through 7 pranks in one week
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will he notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A whole week of pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That means this year's "Prank King" is Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:30.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, saying thank you seems kind of lame
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be a lie to say I'm looking forward to it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You should be able to find them all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because I get screwed over a lot
