Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I would guess this was a trick
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.71,special_Wed_2_X,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\pos(727.5,887)}Sakai Thinks It Was a Trick\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord\b1\3c&H0000D3&}2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm confident in this too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a job to remake a sitcom from the past
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:09:04.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My character was a marriage scammer at a shrimp farm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And was the star of that remake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:10.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You think it's impossible?  \N-Absolutely impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:19.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So many impossible things happened on the set
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:28.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The cameraman was wearing the exact same clothes as someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The dresser gave me a different set of shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They weren't the same. They were from different manufacturers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was thinking "this whole thing is a scam"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai is referring to this sitcom remake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:52.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been on TBS World's Finest Mysteries for a while now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All the shrimp that were raised died...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:10:00.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, it's no longer possible that he'll get everything right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So fast
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:05.08,special_Wed_2_X,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\pos(727.5,887)}Sakai Thinks It Was a Trick{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord\b1\3c&H0000D3&}\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:08.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first time i've visited the neighborhood ramen store
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just moved in a little while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a guy was was supposedly the store manager
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:16.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super busy with all sorts of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I said a bowl of ramen with soy sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He said, "Wait a minute. I'll come back later"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:26.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But then I looked around and realized I was the only customer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Furthermore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:33.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At 6:00 a.m., my intercom rang
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The guy downstairs in my house told me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:42.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You had a fight with a woman yesterday, didn't you? A big one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:47.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't even at home that night
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:51.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the next morning at 6:00 a.m., he rang again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:55.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You brought a girl home again, didn't you? You had a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it was a prank
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a horror story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I always take my clothes to the coin laundry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have a washing machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I turned on the washing machine in the laundry room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And found some unrecognizable old man's clothes in there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not right at all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of life does this guy have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:25.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My new apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There was a pile of human shit under the mailbox
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:33.34,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How does he know it was human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:35.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai has had so many amazing events in his neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,5 consecutive wrong answers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. A great life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:44.58,special_Wed_2_X,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\pos(727.5,887)}Sakai Thinks It Was a Trick\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord\b1\3c&H0000D3&}3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai, who only got one question right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Reveals the last trick
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:52.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone said they wanted me to do a promotion for Tochigi Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let me record the narration for the animation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever worked as a narrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've been called in as a narrator for the regular program
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your voice has great texture
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you said that. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They told me to finish my lines before the scene changes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:15.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The lines that start in the middle of the scene can't be finished until the scene changes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:23.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then read 01:07, 01:13. \N -Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:29.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'd like to recommend two places in Tochigi that you mustn't miss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:34.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First up, the three apes who are known for not looking, not talking, not listening
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:41.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's go to 01:19. \N -Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:47.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First up, the three apes who are known for not looking, not talking, not listening
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The famous three apes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a warning not to listen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't speak unless spoken to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:02.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Keep a straight mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry please pause for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its a little slow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:11.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thee most important part of the description was the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But he made me read it super fast
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:16.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We can't finish this narration without reading it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Read it again, please
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
