Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He did it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you\N  -Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:19.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I read really fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:23.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the other guy said it was OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:27.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's go to 01:30. \N -Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.88,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The second one is a sleeping cat. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was fast... sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry I just feel like I'm reading too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because your own voice feeds back
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I laughed out loud when I heard myself read it so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:54.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,哒哒哒一顿输出然后接下来是睡着的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's the dish in the picture
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's a long line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:04.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bean curd is a soy product, when you make soy milk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:08.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The film formed on the surface of soymilk when cooking is fished out and dried to form
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unlike the flatness of the Kyoto variation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has existed since the Edo period
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:13.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This line has to be said before the interview
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:19.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think the instructions for the thing are necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Know all about bean curd
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.11,0:15:23.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bean curd is a soy product, when you make soy milk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The film formed on the surface of soymilk when cooking is fished out and dried to form
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unlike the flatness of the Kyoto variation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The tofus is rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has existed since the Edo period
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This one's gone again
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Auntie's bean curd
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:36.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The guy at the store said to be sure to add this note
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see. There's no way to cut it down, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry.\N  -It's okay. I'm trying. I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bean curd is a soy product, when you make soy milk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The film formed on the surface of soy milk when cooking is fished out and dried to form
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unlike the flatness of the Kyoto variation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This type is rolled into many layers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And is haracterized by roundness and fullness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has existed since the Edo period
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you very much. \N -Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's a big help.\N  -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He did it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:08.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because the staff is very conscientious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever done this kind of animation before
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, how to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:18.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been called in to record this, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:22.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the result is as follows
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only two of them were right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You got two correct
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So little. Only two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:31.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way! No way! I don't want it to be true
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:40.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which one do you have the most confidence in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Magazine interviews
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right. \N -That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:47.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about. That's suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, what else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The one who complained that I'm noisy is a pain in the ass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The guy who complained about me was horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That we don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't know?
