Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that true? Do I have to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hate it when people like that live downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You also guessed correctly about the narration
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, the narration
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was really exaggerated at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:16.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This presentation is really just the tip of the iceberg
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:19.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are many other places in Nikko that I hope you will visit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:23.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One of the three most famous waterfalls in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:25.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 97-meter-high Huayan Falls
