Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:32.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Iroha-zaka and other sightseeing routes connecting downtown Nikko with Lake Chuzenji and Oku Nikko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.79,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So long
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.17,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
