Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.56,0:38:21.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Won't clean up
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.06,0:38:22.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.26,0:38:23.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm starting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.13,0:38:25.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, that looks so good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.26,0:38:29.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yummy!\N  -Yummy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.76,0:38:30.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.41,0:38:32.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The more I see of this guy, the more he pisses me off
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.93,0:38:32.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Such a happy Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.47,0:38:33.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.77,0:38:34.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So happy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.58,0:38:36.46,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why don't you clean up your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.90,0:38:37.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's make a lot of memories together
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.64,0:38:39.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I baked cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.78,0:38:43.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Really? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.25,0:38:43.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.35,0:38:45.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought you never cooked
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.32,0:38:47.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't, but i'm trying
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.52,0:38:51.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Miku taught me how to bake cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.72,0:38:54.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is Miku up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.15,0:38:55.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Crushed cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.16,0:38:55.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:39:00.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She said "I want to make good memories with cookies"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.06,0:39:03.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, can I smash them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:05.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.57,0:39:06.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wont, I'm just kidding
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:07.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.60,0:39:09.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, that's great. That's really great
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.37,0:39:10.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. You broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.21,0:39:12.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I am truly loved
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:14.08,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can keep watching this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.44,0:39:17.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The end of the year brought Richi's last job as an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.98,0:39:21.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Countdown TV New Year's Eve Program
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.98,0:39:25.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A three-person team
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.35,0:39:27.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.77,0:39:42.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.37,0:39:44.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's finally over
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.13,0:39:50.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Richi is no longer a member
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.21,0:39:52.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard to believe. Wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.05,0:39:55.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been three people every day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.12,0:39:57.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it yet
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.02,0:39:59.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.09,0:40:05.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel real. It's not real, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.33,0:40:07.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's over
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.60,0:40:09.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's over... you worked hard
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.57,0:40:11.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.00,0:40:15.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who made me an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.61,0:40:16.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.46,0:40:17.74,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Last time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.74,0:40:18.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.04,0:40:21.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be going up and down like that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.78,0:40:25.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you only I didn't fall in love with Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:29.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we hope you'll be happy as Kuro-chan's girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.29,0:40:30.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.65,0:40:31.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Be happy.  \N-I'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.51,0:40:37.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so Richi's life as an idol end
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.43,0:40:42.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the recruitment for a new member begins
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.65,0:40:46.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For which over 1,000 resumes were received
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.72,0:40:55.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, Watanabe, the head of WACK, the company in charge, and Kuro-chan reviewed the materials
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.33,0:41:02.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Leading to the first round of selection of 100 cleared candidates
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.25,0:41:04.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many people do you want to add in?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.75,0:41:08.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How many people are good? I'd like to wait until after the selection process
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.89,0:41:11.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you for attending the auditions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.19,0:41:13.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Kuro-chan. He's Watanabe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, first of all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.09,0:41:17.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please introduce yourself and state why you want to join
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.10,0:41:20.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And sing a song that you're good at
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.10,0:41:21.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then please begin
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.88,0:41:25.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sunglasses? Sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.68,0:41:27.09,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.58,0:41:29.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a good relationship with my parents growing up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.05,0:41:32.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i've always wanted to be an idol
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.72,0:41:34.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing sunglasses? \N -Do people still wear sunglasses to auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.32,0:41:35.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've said it since I was in elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.25,0:41:37.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I ended up being laughed at
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.79,0:41:41.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But my parents laughed at me the most for what I wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.79,0:41:44.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's why I cut them off yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:46.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:49.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened, but i'm here today
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.59,0:41:50.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.13,0:41:51.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One verse, please
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.63,0:41:59.33,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Underestimating the business, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.88,0:42:04.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, what does Riko look like with her glasses off?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.82,0:42:09.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll take off my glasses. Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:11.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not bad. But also cute with glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.69,0:42:14.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But also a beautiful girl with glasses off. \N -Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.12,0:42:18.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I kinda like the girl with the glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.00,0:42:22.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You work as a caregiver, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.45,0:42:24.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm a caregiver
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.50,0:42:26.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let me give you an analogy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.04,0:42:29.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If I cry, can you show me how you'll stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.47,0:42:30.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.00,0:42:31.11,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.28,0:42:36.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan, what's wrong? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.25,0:42:37.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My toys were taken
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.61,0:42:39.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, your toys were taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:41.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see. Then I'll give you a new toy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.22,0:42:44.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What kind of toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.52,0:42:45.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bubu toys
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.36,0:42:47.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's a "bubu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.52,0:42:49.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bubu's a car. Have you ever been in one?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.03,0:42:51.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've never been in one. It's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.63,0:42:54.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then let's sit together. It's not scary when you're with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.60,0:42:56.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I won't cry anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:42:58.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.87,0:43:00.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:02.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From that point
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.71,0:43:04.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.77,0:43:06.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,6 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.34,0:43:08.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Six years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.21,0:43:08.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.21,0:43:11.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kuro-chan, long time no see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.31,0:43:13.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think you've forgotten about me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.75,0:43:15.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Long time no see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.35,0:43:18.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We've had dinner together about five times
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.29,0:43:19.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also went to karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.09,0:43:20.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.94,0:43:26.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Kuro-chan was respectful and didn't try to hit on me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.83,0:43:27.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't make a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.83,0:43:29.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, wait a minute. Five times?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.93,0:43:34.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We had okonomiyaki at BochiBochi in Ebisu
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.00,0:43:37.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And went to Shibuya to play darts
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.14,0:43:39.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then back to Kuro-chan's place
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.21,0:43:38.87,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Serious dating
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.74,0:43:40.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, we went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.91,0:43:46.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, i'd usually play darts after going to BochiBochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.52,0:43:47.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gold package?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.98,0:43:51.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then take someone home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.65,0:43:52.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Trying to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.86,0:43:56.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must have been tempted at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.54,0:44:01.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, these 10 made the first cut
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.55,0:44:04.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Successfully shortlisted for the second selection
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.15,0:44:05.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Out of 1,000 people, 10 stood out
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.20,0:44:10.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are 10 people left
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.14,0:44:12.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How are you going to screen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.94,0:44:16.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For today, I'd like to keep half of them, five of them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.71,0:44:18.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Select five
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.11,0:44:20.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then decide
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.78,0:44:22.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.52,0:44:25.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to sing?\N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.29,0:44:32.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can we stop for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.50,0:44:34.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you sing more popular tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.10,0:44:37.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.23,0:44:38.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.13,0:44:40.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's a good singer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.86,0:44:47.68,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A good singer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.45,0:44:55.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems kinda good...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.95,0:44:57.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But didn't stand out very much
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.66,0:44:59.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Judging seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.95,0:45:00.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm 16 years old, I'm a freshman in high school, and my name is Izuki
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.39,0:45:06.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Senior year, you're still young
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.46,0:45:09.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you put your hair back?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.42,0:45:13.15,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A real audition
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.04,0:45:17.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your face is so small
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.14,0:45:18.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.01,0:45:19.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like a little bean \N -Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.37,0:45:22.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:26.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I ask, are you wearing something underneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.25,0:45:29.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.69,0:45:30.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.25,0:45:31.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No... I just wasn't sure
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.45,0:45:34.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thought you wanted a challenge today
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.42,0:45:36.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter either way
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.16,0:45:44.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Longer hair
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.07,0:45:46.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What does it look like tied back?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.87,0:45:50.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.10,0:45:50.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's just the way he likes it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.74,0:45:52.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Very cute, very cute
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.54,0:45:53.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Beauty queen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.94,0:45:55.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.55,0:45:57.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's up to me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.15,0:46:02.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.69,0:46:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.02,0:46:12.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a panty check
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.26,0:46:16.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Giant's Sadaharu Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.47,0:46:17.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What'll it be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.96,0:46:21.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Imitating him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.72,0:46:23.26,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.94,0:46:24.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its like that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.68,0:46:36.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, i'll announce the results of the second selection
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.22,0:46:38.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First is...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.55,0:46:45.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Chihiro, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.71,0:46:43.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.50,0:46:46.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In second place
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.10,0:46:52.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sachiko, congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.47,0:46:56.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Izuki, congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.74,0:47:01.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nozomi, congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.36,0:47:00.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shimada
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.95,0:47:03.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, don't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.04,0:47:08.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kino, congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.74,0:47:12.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So these five made it to the final stage
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.80,0:47:19.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which of them will become the newest member?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.58,0:47:27.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the decision will be made at a later date
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.66,0:47:35.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Plus there will be some footage of Richi and Kuro-chan's New Years holiday
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.06,0:47:38.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.33,0:47:42.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So reluctant!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.28,0:48:14.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching. Support me and get subs early at patreon.com/zwanster03

